 2. Y. Zhu, A.I. Hawari, "Implementation of a Generalized Coherent  72 1451     
    Elastic Scattering Formulation for Thermal Neutron Scattering   72 1451     
    Analysis," Proceedings of ICNC 2015: 35th International         72 1451     
    Conference on Nuclear Criticality Safety (2015)                 72 1451     
 3. V.F. Sears, "Neutron Scattering Lengths and Cross Sections"     72 1451     
    Neutron News, 3, 3 (1992) 29.                                   72 1451     
